name: JUMP TO THE MOON!
description:
Mini game made  for 130 Mini Jam (a 3-day game jam based on the limitation of 10 seconds)

Click on the falling stars to help the rabbit reach the moon.  There are 6 levels available, each lasting 10 seconds.  Hit all the stars to enter the next level.
